org.energy_home.jemma.zgd
Interface IGatewayEventManager

All Known Implementing Classes:
GatewayEventManager
public interface IGatewayEventManager

Dispatches Gateway Device Events to registered listeners. This class is called by the Data Layer to notify Device Events when they happens.

The GalController maintains a collection of registered event's listeners. All possible events are those provided by GatewayEventListener.

When an event happens, the Gal controller sends it to the relevant notifier method, one of those present in this class.

Author:
"Ing. Marco Nieddu or from Consoft Sistemi S.P.A., financed by EIT ICT Labs activity SecSES - Secure Energy Systems (activity id 13030)"
